        <p>The maintenance and inventory component of HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade allows the
            administrator to install, configure, and manage the hosts of the HP Helion OpenStack
            Carrier Grade cluster. </p>
        <p><b>Managing Hosts</b></p>
